arStrings.szText: "What are we doing in this place?"
Just—just listen. Varshan is the source of the disease, but I can cure him. I just need to find the correct ritual.
Talking fast. Anxious, but still determined and optimistic. "Vahr-shn."
These ruins have been sealed since the Zakarum first arrived. If there’s anywhere to hunt for lost knowledge, it’s got to be here.
Anxious, but still determined and optimistic.
